text:
One, two, three, four...
Just make sure not to overlap with the person in front...

Producer! Good work
 Are you okay coming here?

Yeah, I'm fine.
It's almost time, but are you ready?

...Yes.
I don't intend to match perfectly with everyone anymore.

If everyone moves exactly the same,
anyone could do it, right?
I want to see Hiori's dance.

I'll show you
the dance of 283PRO's Hiori Kazano.
